title: You're Acting Like A Genuine Ass - EP5
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


Are animals gay?, Top 10 gayest animals, Are dogs gay? Sal and Chris figure out if they would be BEARS in the homosexual community, The boys talk bad body hair, Letting your inner gay out is so much fun, Sal buys a bad outfit and unveils it on the show, Sal never takes tags off new clothes, Sals cousin used to steal from stores by buying and returning clothes, shoplifting stories, Sal talks about moments he couldn't control himself on Impractical Jokers shoots and then a few horror stories from going to Catholic schools.


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
